        "TileImage": "$($repository 5403294c-5390-46ba-a246-4bb6108253c0).Image",
        "Description": "Patrick Carlisle needs his inhertence, and he needs it now.  Alexa is too strong of a woman to have died from the posion in her and Zachary&apos;s dinner that evening, but Patrick will make sure he gets the job done this time.  His father and Uncle only stand in the way of what is rightfully his and the Carlisle lineage.  And of course to eliminate any paper trail, the detective that they hired to investigate Zachary&apos;s death must go as well.",
